-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/menses-missed-sawm-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":26807,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women make up missed fasts, not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen we were afflicted with menstruation, we were ordered to make up missed fasts but not missed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 335 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26807","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26807"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26807\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26807"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadi